Package org.demoiselle.signer.chain.icp.brasil.provider Description

Implements providers of ICP-Brasil Chain of Certificate Authorities. Any provider must implement ProviderCA.

Providers available:

  • Keystore provider (ICPBrasilProviderCA)
  • ITI provider (ICPBrasilOnLineITIProviderCA)
  • SERPRO provider (ICPBrasilOnLineSerproProviderCA)
  • File ACcompactado.zip (ICPBrasilUserHomeProviderCA)
